name: TRIKARYOTE ORGANISM 10
description:
These are the TRIKARYOTES. 

Created [27-10-17] Experiments with Trapcode TAO to create new categories of basic organisms different from prokaryotes and eukaryotes. They don't have a defined nucleus and they are made of angular geometric segments. There will be several trikaryotes organisms to collect. By collecting 10 different specimen unlock your new personalized trikaryote forever associated with your name. 

New output | 1:1 | 1080x1080 | 120 frames | 24fps

This last specimen of the collection had first died during incubation and then it was mysteriously reborn and multiplied. It gained a new mutation making it immune to first market tier pricing. I will have to give them away a 0 tezos. They want to spread.
10 of you will have the opportunity to gather the whole series of 10 specimens.
